 Henry Emile Agbai was born on 21 September 1984 in Aba Abia state. Also known as Email, is a Nigerian Entertainer, Chief Executive Director of Titans Paint Limited, and CEO of Titians studio channel. Agbai was born in Abia state, raised in Aba in a family of six, having three siblings. Raised by both parents. His dad was a CEO of a company where he imported sea can foods in the early 80s and 90s. Agbai was born on the 21st of September 1984 and is currently 37 years. He is from a family of 6, having two brothers and a sister. All from the same parents. He is currently married to a beautiful woman and together they have two amazing kids, a daughter, and a son. His primary education was at Cornerstone academy, then he moved to St. Patrick’s model primary and secondary school, where he Lastly graduated from Abia State University where He studied Theatre Arts Agbai worth one million dollars owns and runs a paint company, Titan Paints, a movie production company, Titan Studio Channel, both in Lagos, and a unisex salon, Zephyr Beauty Home, as well in Benin City. For now, he was awarded an Award of donor – Police college, and Award of support – Dominion city church. Award nominee – City people magazine.